Package: logilab-packaging
Architecture: all
Suggests: logilab-doctools, pymacs, emacsen-common, debian-archive-keyring
Recommends: mercurial (>= 0.9.3), subversion, debinstall, diffstat
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python, python-debian, lintian, pbuilder, devscripts, debhelper,
         python-logilab-common, sudo, cdebootstrap, python-apt
Conflicts: devtools, simh, python-vcslib
Replaces: devtools, python-vcslib
Description: set of development tools used at Logilab
 Set of tools which aims to help the developpement process, including :
  * tools to check and build source and/or Debian packages
  * standard for zope and Python packages

Package: logilab-elisp
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, emacsen-common
Conflicts: devtools
Replaces: devtools
Description: emacs lisp code for logilab development tools
 Set of elisp goodies including :
  * an emacs mode for pycover files
  * an emacs mode for ChangeLog files
  * a small set of emacs shortcuts used at logilab

Package: narval-lgp
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, cubicweb-apycot, narval-apycot, logilab-packaging (= ${source:Version})
Description: lgp extensions for apycot
 This package provides a set of actions to run lgp check and build from
 Narval/Apycot.
